title: From Ellen to music videos: Vancouver kids show off mad dancing skills
text: From Ellen to music videos: Vancouver kids show off mad dancing skills Vancouver-based dancing duo Lucky Aces first charmed Ellen DeGeneres before helping producer Sigala climb to number 1 on the U.K. charts with his new track. Reporter David Friend rounds up the best in this week's entertainment. October 4, 2015 10:14 AM
